### Angular / Web
- Signals mandatory: signal(), computed(), effect() — never BehaviorSubject
- Injection: always inject(), never constructor injection
- HTTP: always RepoHttp (not HttpClient directly)
- Styles: CSS theme variables (--color-*) — see docs/frontend-ui-ux-guidelines.md
- No hardcoded Tailwind: never text-blue-500, always text-(--color-primary)
